game.name: Horace and Cheese
game.description:
This time you are welcome here with a completely brand new arcade challenge where you have to put your shooting abilities to the test. A little mouse named Horace is waiting for your helping hand. Join Horace Vs Cheese and get ready to help him to grab the cheese in all the levels! These cheese bites are far away from him. You have to aim and shoot Horace the Hamster into the cheese by using the limited moves. Guide him to eat all of them to earn 3 stars!

Drag Horace to aim and then release to launch to the cheese! Try to complete your task with more accuracy to get 3 stars rating and extra cheese bonus and shots bonus points! When you complete each level, you can also track your present and high score on the screen. Click the next button to move to the advanced level or replay button to try this level again! Remember you have limited moves to get the job done so be careful while aiming your target. 

Once Horace collects all of the cheese, make sure to land him safely to his house. Play wisely to complete all levels and earn maximum stars and use those stars to upgrade other popular characters like Bessie, Rock Monster, Flora, Cherry, Custard and Mr Blue! This cute html5 shooting puzzle includes 30 unique and engaging levels coupled with multiple characters and bonus systems. Avoid moldy cheese to protect your life from losing! Check out more jump physics games for kids that you can enjoy online without download!
